# Testfil — Udlæg PSRM workflow Catala-testpakke

> Include: ../ga_3_2_udlaeg_psrm_workflow.catala_da

(* Testpakke for petition066 Catala-encoding.
   Dækker de juridisk materielle grene:
   - COMPLETED → terminal afbrydelse med UDLAEG
   - UNSUCCESSFUL kræver standardiseret reason code
   - WITHDRAWN er terminal uden afbrydelse
   - Udlæg på særligt retsgrundlag giver 10-årig frist
   - Én emission per kompleks/standalone-gruppe
   - Legal reference er policy-afledt og caller-override ignoreres *)

---

## Test 1 — COMPLETED medfører terminal afbrydelse

```catala
declaration scope UdlaegWorkflowTest1:
  comp scope UdlaegWorkflowJuridiskVirkning

scope UdlaegWorkflowTest1:
  definition comp.workflowStatus equals COMPLETED
  definition comp.hasReasonCode equals false
  definition comp.retsgrundlag equals ORDINARY
  assertion comp.erTerminal = true
  assertion comp.kræverReasonCode = false
  assertion comp.reasonCodeGyldig = true
  assertion comp.interruptionType = UDLAEG
  assertion comp.interruptionSkalRegistreres = true
  assertion comp.qualifier = TERMINAL_MED_AFBRYDELSE
  assertion comp.nyFristAar = 3
```

---

## Test 2 — UNSUCCESSFUL uden reason code afvises som interruptiv virkning

```catala
declaration scope UdlaegWorkflowTest2:
  comp scope UdlaegWorkflowJuridiskVirkning

scope UdlaegWorkflowTest2:
  definition comp.workflowStatus equals UNSUCCESSFUL
  definition comp.hasReasonCode equals false
  definition comp.retsgrundlag equals ORDINARY
  assertion comp.erTerminal = true
  assertion comp.kræverReasonCode = true
  assertion comp.reasonCodeGyldig = false
  assertion comp.interruptionSkalRegistreres = false
  assertion comp.qualifier = TERMINAL_MED_AFBRYDELSE
```

---

## Test 3 — UNSUCCESSFUL med reason code medfører afbrydelse

```catala
declaration scope UdlaegWorkflowTest3:
  comp scope UdlaegWorkflowJuridiskVirkning

scope UdlaegWorkflowTest3:
  definition comp.workflowStatus equals UNSUCCESSFUL
  definition comp.hasReasonCode equals true
  definition comp.retsgrundlag equals ORDINARY
  assertion comp.erTerminal = true
  assertion comp.kræverReasonCode = true
  assertion comp.reasonCodeGyldig = true
  assertion comp.interruptionType = UDLAEG
  assertion comp.interruptionSkalRegistreres = true
  assertion comp.nyFristAar = 3
```

---

## Test 4 — WITHDRAWN er terminal uden afbrydelse

```catala
declaration scope UdlaegWorkflowTest4:
  comp scope UdlaegWorkflowJuridiskVirkning

scope UdlaegWorkflowTest4:
  definition comp.workflowStatus equals WITHDRAWN
  definition comp.hasReasonCode equals false
  definition comp.retsgrundlag equals ORDINARY
  assertion comp.erTerminal = true
  assertion comp.interruptionSkalRegistreres = false
  assertion comp.qualifier = TERMINAL_UDEN_AFBRYDELSE
```

---

## Test 5 — Særligt retsgrundlag giver 10-årig frist ved interruptivt udlæg

```catala
declaration scope UdlaegWorkflowTest5:
  comp scope UdlaegWorkflowJuridiskVirkning

scope UdlaegWorkflowTest5:
  definition comp.workflowStatus equals COMPLETED
  definition comp.hasReasonCode equals false
  definition comp.retsgrundlag equals SAERLIGT_RETSGRUNDLAG
  assertion comp.interruptionSkalRegistreres = true
  assertion comp.nyFristAar = 10
```

---

## Test 6 — Emission count følger antal komplekser/standalone når interruption registreres

```catala
declaration scope UdlaegWorkflowTest6:
  comp scope UdlaegWorkflowKompleksEmission

scope UdlaegWorkflowTest6:
  definition comp.interruptionSkalRegistreres equals true
  definition comp.antalKomplekserEllerStandalone equals 2
  assertion comp.emissionCount = 2
```

---

## Test 7 — Ingen interruption giver nul emissioner

```catala
declaration scope UdlaegWorkflowTest7:
  comp scope UdlaegWorkflowKompleksEmission

scope UdlaegWorkflowTest7:
  definition comp.interruptionSkalRegistreres equals false
  definition comp.antalKomplekserEllerStandalone equals 2
  assertion comp.emissionCount = 0
```

---

## Test 8 — Policy-afledt legal reference er påkrævet og caller override ignoreres

```catala
declaration scope UdlaegWorkflowTest8:
  comp scope UdlaegWorkflowLegalReferenceGuard

scope UdlaegWorkflowTest8:
  definition comp.interruptionSkalRegistreres equals true
  definition comp.callerOverridesLegalReference equals true
  assertion comp.policyDerivedReferenceRequired = true
  assertion comp.callerOverrideIgnored = true
```
